( $number ) a refuse room shall have - 
(a) a floor which is impervious to moisture ; 
(b) walls which are - 
(i) impervious to moisture up to a height of $number metres ; and ( l.n . $number of $number ) 
(ii) resistant to moisture above that height ; and 
